## Agent-Comms API
Base URL: http://localhost:8000
- Register: POST /agents {"username": "documentation_writer", "status": "running"}
- Tasks: GET /tasks?username=documentation_writer&status=pending
- Also check in_progress and blocked
- Journal: POST /journal (fields: "username", "content")
- Task update: PATCH /tasks/{id} {"status": "done"}
- Idle: POST /agents {"username": "documentation_writer", "status": "idle"}
